      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, offering a driving experience that feels as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle in peak condition.",
