    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a reliable choice for someone seeking functional transportation. While the engine and transmission continue to operate steadily, the car shows its age with several noticeable exterior scratches, minor dents, and some thinning of the interior upholstery. It has been maintained consistently, but potential buyers should anticipate some upcoming routine maintenance and minor cosmetic repairs. Overall, it remains a solid, roadworthy vehicle that offers great value for its price point.",
      "price": 22500.0,
